<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Don't break existing functionality</title>
    <para>
        Any commit should leave the respository integrity intact. After a commit none of the previously committed
        functionality should be broken. You should thus always make an update and run all tests before committing.
    </para>
</section>    